      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable daily driver that's ready for its next adventure? This vehicle is in honest, fair condition and offers a fantastic opportunity to own a reliable car at a great price! While you'll find some typical signs of use and character from its time on the road, it remains a solid choice for anyone needing practical transportation. Come take a look and see how this car can fit your lifestyle!",
