    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing exactly as it did when it first left the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like shine without a single chip or scratch, and the wheels are entirely free of curb rash. Inside, the cabin is pristine; the leather upholstery is supple and shows no signs of wear, and all electronic features function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in peak condition, providing a smooth, quiet, and powerful driving experience that feels brand new.",
      "price": 48900.0,
